        "subject": "LU-3326 ofd: wait for object destory for -ENOPSC",
        "message": "LU-3326 ofd: wait for object destory for -ENOPSC\n\nin ofd, the IO requests on those object being destroyed by\nofd_destroy will prevent it to destroy (the clients holding\nthe extent lock), which affect the normal IO requests and\ncould cause -ENOSPC.\n\nChange-Id: Ia246122a5c3471b7cbea9cdaa7fad2ea4db856c5\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\n"
